<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">Alpha &middot; Approaching Beta &middot; MIT Licensed</div>
  <h1>Open-source .NET tooling<br/>for VS Code.</h1>
  <p class="tagline">
    Forge is an early .NET language tooling stack with a Rust LSP host,
    Roslyn-powered C# features, solution navigation, NuGet workflows,
    and profiler tooling in the VS Code extension.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="/docs/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/MelbourneDeveloper/forge" class="btn btn-secondary">GitHub</a>
  </div>
</section>

